rmal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9885f2be487983219eac7d72c904d9e1f8e514b2","tid":166610,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個人自殺死左 <br />\n只係將佢自己既唔開心  <br />\n轉移到其他關心佢既人身上 <br />\n<br />\n當然 ,  如果一個人活於世上,  無家人無朋友無男女朋友無同事等等 ... 佢自殺死又真係無可厚非 ...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一雙手只要握成拳頭能捱下去<br />\n哪怕我面容極蒼白拒絕疲累</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然 陳詠謙 好多詞都好柒.  但依首係唔錯, 好有鼓勵性"},{"pid":"e7c340637cbd3c6418631b69c4295e3b1fef124f","tid":166610,"uid":56677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fdc01ae4057d41a689acf293b20aa83833e11a","tid":166610,"uid":9466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只係有時我會諗 如果佢真係好想死 已經諗得好清楚既 仲應唔應該阻止佢 如果阻止佢 咁我地係咪好自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 生命誠可貴</blockquote><br />\n咁唔好用跳樓呢個方式得唔得？<br />\n跳樓對於路人危險性真係好高"},{"pid":"ad96c860b49b22e8638aff852e32a5d5d5515a3a","tid":166610,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個人自殺死左 <br />\n只係將佢自己既唔開心  <br />\n轉移到其他關心佢既人身上 <br />\n<br />\n當然 ,  如果一個人活於世上,  無家人無朋友無男女朋友無同事等等 ... 佢自殺死又真係無可厚非 ...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一雙手只要握成拳頭能捱下去<br />\n哪怕我面容極蒼白拒絕疲累</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然 陳詠謙 好多詞都好柒.  但依首係唔錯, 好有鼓勵性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢啲詞幾過癮吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc9b14242a504a6e6b0a9b4531a61079039abef","tid":166610,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u53JbE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u53JbE.png&h=ff3d8cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/en400ao.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fen400ao.png&h=c12d68c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47dccfc8949086bef64d8a6eee014e7d3c02bc2e","tid":166610,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"2f470ec64f67d03011ea30392f905bc517d7b64e","tid":166610,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個人自殺死左 <br />\n只係將佢自己既唔開心  <br />\n轉移到其他關心佢既人身上 <br />\n<br />\n當然 ,  如果一個人活於世上,  無家人無朋友無男女朋友無同事等等 ... 佢自殺死又真係無可厚非 ...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一雙手只要握成拳頭能捱下去<br />\n哪怕我面容極蒼白拒絕疲累</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然 陳詠謙 好多詞都好柒.  但依首係唔錯, 好有鼓勵性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最鍾意<br />\n寫你太難"},{"pid":"02a0c8b8bc518c23bba63b61c97903e392b7a0ea","tid":166610,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第一句已笑<br />\nSorry<br />\n唔係話想人跳樓<br />\n但係你句野太誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係有流淚<br />\n最勁果2次係<br />\nMegabox果單同<br />\n單親的13歲男孩...彩福果單<br />\n<br />\n都有崩潰左30分鐘...<br />\n可惜佢地...點解要咁傻豬仔.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解？<br />\n點解死=唔好？<br />\n我會可惜，但係只係出於自己仲在人世，而相識嘅人唔喺度嘅傷感，而唔係覺得自殺死就係傻</blockquote><br />\n世界上有好多人生不如死<br />\n<br />\n但係生物本能要你覺得死係可怕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要自殺者苟且求存只為令旁觀者安心，唔同咁就唔自私咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持安樂死"},{"pid":"2cabaa48ca31cf46c0612c3db899fdab2490c063","tid":166610,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"以上只統計學生, 未計其他人士"},{"pid":"47ae05948eb77e05c